y did not show up. AEK Athens had also -3 points because of a case of fixing games in the previous season.\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n{{winners||[[Super League Greece|Alpha Ethniki]] 1986\u201387<br>Champions|[[File:600px Quadrado Branco com uma figura olimpica grega.PNG|150px]]<br>[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]|25th}}\n\n==Results==\n{{#invoke:sports results|main\n|matches_style=FBR|solid_cell=grey\n|team1=AEK|team2=APA|team3=APK|team4=ARI|team5=DIA\n|team6=DOX|team7=ETH|team8=IRA|team9=LAR|team10=OFI\n|team11=OLY|team12=PAO|team13=PAN|team14=PAOK|team15=PAS\n|team16=VER\n\n|name_AEK=[[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n|match_AEK_APA=2\u20132\n|match_AEK_APK=2\u20130\n|match_AEK_ARI=1\u20130\n|match_AEK_DIA={{red|0\u20130}}\n|match_AEK_DOX=1\u20131\n|match_AEK_ETH=2\u20131\n|match_AEK_IRA={{red|0\u20130}}\n|match_AEK_LAR=1\u20130\n|match_AEK_OFI=0\u20131\n|match_AEK_OLY=0\u20131\n|match_AEK_PAO=0\u20133\n|match_AEK_PAN=1\u20131\n|match_AEK_PAOK=1\u20132\n|match_AEK_PAS=2\u20131\n|match_AEK_VER=5\u20130\n\n|name_APA=[[Apollon Smyrni F.C.|Apollon Athens]]\n|match_APA_AEK=1\u20131\n|match_APA_APK=0\u20131\n|match_APA_ARI={{red|0\u20130}}\n|match_APA_DIA=1\u20131\n|match_APA_DOX=1\u20131\n|match_APA_ETH=1\u20130\n|match_APA_IRA=0\u20130\n|match_APA_LAR=1\u20130\n|match_APA_OFI=1\u20131\n|match_APA_OLY=1\u20133\n|match_APA_PAO=0\u20132\n|match_APA_PAN=0\u20132\n|match_APA_PAOK=2\u20130\n|match_APA_PAS=0\u20130\n|match_APA_VER=1\u20130\n\n|name_APK=[[Apollon Pontou FC|Apollon Kalamarias]]\n|match_APK_AEK=0\u20132\n|match_APK_APA=4\u20131\n|match_APK_ARI=1\u20135\n|match_APK_DIA=0\u20130\n|match_APK_DOX=1\u20130\n|match_APK_ETH=1\u20131\n|match_APK_IRA=1\u20133\n|match_APK_LAR=0\u20132\n|match_APK_OFI=1\u20130\n|match_APK_OLY=0\u20131\n|match_APK_PAO=2\u20130\n|match_APK_PAN={{red|0\u20132}}\n|match_APK_PAOK=0\u20130\n|match_APK_PAS=1\u20130\n|match_APK_VER={{red|0\u20130}}\n\n|name_ARI=[[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]\n|match_ARI_AEK=1\u20133\n|match_ARI_APA=0\u20131\n|match_ARI_AP