] runner-up: [[2015 AFC Asian Cup|2015]]<ref name=\"Asian Cup final\"/>\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[Bundesliga]] Young Player of the Hinrunde: [[2010\u201311 Bundesliga|2010]]<ref>{{cite web |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101025042/http://www.bundesliga.de/de/liga/news/2010/index.php?f=0000171384.php |archive-date=1 January 2011 |url=http://www.bundesliga.de/de/liga/news/2010/index.php?f=0000171384.php |title=Das Deb\u00fct der Hinrunde: Heung-Min Son (Hamburger SV) |language=de |publisher=Bundesliga |access-date=14 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Korea Football Association#Awards|Korean Footballer of the Year]]: 2013, 2014, 2017, 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/bulletin/2014/01/24/0200000000AKR20140124133251007.HTML |script-title=ko:\uc190\ud765\ubbfc \ucd95\uad6c\ud611\ud68c \uc120\uc815 \uc62c\ud574\uc758 \uc120\uc218 |language=ko |agency=Yonhap News Agency |date=24 January 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/bulletin/2014/12/23/0200000000AKR20141223096200007.HTML?input=1195m|script-title=ko:\uc190\ud765\ubbfc 2\ub144 \uc5f0\uc18d \ub300\ud55c\ucd95\uad6c\ud611\ud68c \uc62c\ud574\uc758 \uc120\uc218 |language=ko |agency=Yonhap News Agency |date=23 December 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.the-afc.com/news/afcsection/son-heung-min-wins-third-korea-republic-male-player-of-the-year-award |title=Son Heung-min wins third Korea Republic Male Player of the Year award |publisher=Asian Football Confederation |date=20 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kfa.or.kr/layer_popup/popup_live.php?act=news_tv_detail&idx=22183&div_code=news&check_url=bGF5ZXI=&lang=KOR |script-title=ko:2019 KFA \uc2dc\uc0c1\uc2dd \uac1c\ucd5c...\uc190\ud765\ubbfc-\uc9c0\uc18c\uc5f0 \uc62c\ud574\uc758 \uc120\uc218 |publisher=Korea Football Association |date=19 December 2019 |access-date=19 December 2019 |language=ko}}</ref>\n*[[Best Footballer in Asia]]: [[Best Footballer in Asia 2014|2014]], [[Best Footballer in Asia 20