ancefootball.fr/news/Les-dix-lecons-a-retenir-de-la-liste-des-30-du-ballon-d-or-france-football-2019/1072160 |title=Les dix le\u00e7ons \u00e0 retenir de la liste des 30 du Ballon d'Or France Football 2019 |website=France Football |language=fr |date=21 October 2019 |accessdate=23 October 2019}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Champions League]] Team of the Group Stage: [[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League|2019\u201320]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2635838.html |title=Champions League Fantasy Team of the Group stage |publisher=UEFA |date=14 December 2019 |accessdate=14 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]] Goal of the Decade: 2020<ref>{{cite web |title=Heung-Min Son wins Goal of the Decade |publisher=Tottenham Hotspur F.C. |url=https://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/2020/january/heung-min-son-wins-goal-of-the-decade/ |date=1 January 2020 |accessdate=5 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/first-team-squad/heung-min-son/ Profile] at the Tottenham Hotspur F.C. website\n*{{FIFA player}}\n*{{AFC player|28669}}\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Tottenham Hotspur F.C. squad}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = South Korea squads\n| bg = #C21E2B\n| fg = white\n| bordercolor = #2E20BF\n| list1 = \n{{South Korea squad 2011 AFC Asian Cup}}\n{{South Korea squad 2014 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{South Korea squad 2015 AFC Asian Cup}}\n{{South Korea men's football squad 2016 Summer Olympics}}\n{{South Korea squad 2018 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{South Korea squad 2019 AFC Asian Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards\n| bg = gold\n| fg = navy\n| list1 = \n{{2015 AFC Asian Cup Team of the Tournament}}\n{{Korea Football Association Footballer of the Year}}\n{{AFC Asian International Player of the Year}}\n{{Best Footballer in Asia}}\n{{Tottenham Hotspur F.C. Player of the Year}}\n{{Forbes Korea Power Celebrity}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Son, Heung-min}}\n[[Category:1992 births]