hniki was replaced by [[Superleague Greece]].\n\n{{Location map+ |Greece |width=380 |float=center |caption=Location of teams in '''1989\u201390 Alpha Ethniki''' |places=\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=37.966667 |long=23.716667 |label=<small>[[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]</small><br><small>[[Apollon Smyrni F.C.|Apollon]]</small><br><small>[[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]]</small><br><small>[[Panionios F.C.|Panionios]]</small>}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=40.65     |long=22.9      |label=<small>[[Apollon Kalamarias F.C.|Apollon]]</small><br><small>[[Aris F.C. (Thessaloniki)|Aris]]</small><br><small>[[Iraklis Thessaloniki F.C.|Iraklis]]</small><br><small>[[PAOK F.C.|PAOK]]</small>}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=37.95     |long=23.633333 |label=<small>[[Ethnikos Piraeus F.C.|Ethnikos]]</small><br><small>[[Ionikos F.C.|Ionikos]]</small><br><small>[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]</small> |position=left}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=41.15     |long=24.133333 |label=<small>[[Doxa Drama F.C.|Doxa]]</small> |position=top}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=39.641667 |long=22.416667 |label=<small>[[AEL 1964 FC|Larissa]]</small> |position=left}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=38.433333 |long=22.866667 |label=<small>[[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]]</small> |position=right}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=35.333333 |long=25.133333 |label=<small>[[OFI Crete|OFI]]</small>}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=39.366667 |long=22.933333 |label=<small>[[Ethnikos Olympiakos Volos F.C.|Olympiakos V.]]</small>}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=41.083333 |long=23.55     |label=<small>[[Panserraikos F.C.|Panserraikos]]</small> |position=left}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=41.133333 |long=24.883333 |label=<small>[[Skoda Xanthi F.C.|Xanthi]]</small>}}\n}}\n\n==League standings==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|show_limit = 5\n|winpoints=2\n|res_col_header=QR\n\n|team1=PAT|name_PAT=[[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]]\n|team2=AEK|name_AEK=[[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n|team3=PAOK